#

Chunky Guacamole with Tomatoes and Onions

10 min
$5
160 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerSnackSimple

Description

A fresh, creamy guacamole bursting with vibrant flavors from tomatoes and onions, perfect for dipping or as a topping.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • medium tomatoes: 1
  • red onion: 1/4
  • lime: 1
  • cilantro: 1/4 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
